		<id>/index.php/2009/11/beginning-stages-of-a-dr-plan-for-sql-se/#comment-2165</id>
		<updated>2009-11-23T09:28:42Z</updated>
		<published>2009-11-23T09:28:42Z</published>
		<content type="html" xml:base="/index.php/datamgmt/datadesign/beginning-stages-of-a-dr-plan-for-sql-se/#comment-2165"><![CDATA[<p>Yeah MJ, we have the same system here.  And try as I might they wont be budged on this.  </p>
<p>My coments being that if every thing failed on this site we could just switch to a replicated of log shiped dr server.  </p>
<p>There coments being, we if every thing failed here we would have no app servers any way, so would need to rebuild the whole thing off site any way.</p>
]]></content>
