		<content type="html" xml:base="/index.php/datamgmt/datadesign/beginning-stages-of-a-dr-plan-for-sql-se/#comment-2170"><![CDATA[<p>Thanks!  This model as served me well for a lot of years.  Always seems easier to plan on levels like this.</p>
<p>The cloud changed a lot of things with DR.  To me it&#8217;s application for DR is the strong points of the cloud.  The type of data being secured makes a huge difference in the concepts but can really make for a cost advantage for DR</p>
]]></content>
